Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.70,0:21:46.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}放到最后再说吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.62,0:21:50.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}现实中满是不如意
Dialogue: 3,0:21:51.04,0:21:55.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子里
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.92,0:21:58.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}准备好参加派对了吗?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一个故事就要开始了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数气泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.52,0:22:09.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数气泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.98,0:22:16.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无论是爸爸妈妈的事
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.53,0:22:18.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}还是闷在心底的回忆
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.78,0:22:23.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都会化作气泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.62,0:22:25.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣忧愁又烦恼
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数往事多纷扰
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都没关系的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事尽怀抱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞进瓶子使劲摇
Dialogue: 3,0:22:37.05,0:22:41.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}噗嗤全部释放　大家一起欢笑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.43,0:22:44.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}咕噜噜　瞬间满是气泡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------Title----------
